message.entry: First argument must be a real full matrix of type single or double.
With the ByRows option, inputs must be 2-D.
With the ByRows option, the DataScale value must be either: a scalar, or a vector with one element per column of the input matrix.
Tolerance value must be a real, full, positive numeric scalar of type single or double.
'DataScale' value must be a positive numeric scalar or vector of type single or double.
Unknown option specified. See the help for a list of valid options.
